al/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做gym就好打？笑話<br />\n利申 有做gym同打過排泰拳</blockquote><br />\n靈活度緊要過你大隻啦<br />\n唔識出拳出腳 同鬼佬打爛仔交輸8成<br />\n人地天生戰鬥型過黃種人n倍</blockquote><br />\n打過先知好打嘅身形（著衫嘅李小龍）vs 唔會想同佢打交嘅身形 （著短衫嘅the rock）vs  打到自己入廠都叫打贏嘅身形（香港之星）<br />\n<br />\n實際街頭上，<br />\n普通人睇打拳撚<br />\n睇落去唔知打唔打得，打完先知好抽得。（普通人入廠，打拳撚比黑警拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n普通人睇gym撚<br />\n咁撚大隻，同佢打冇著數，調頭跑走。（世界和平，冇人入廠唔洗比人拉）<br />\n<br />\n打拳撚都知比賽有分磅數，係街頭上更加唔會越級挑戰gym撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> gym撚普遍都係中量級、重量級75kg以上，香港打拳撚大多數係65kg以下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結論，街頭開片，做gym幫你贏在開打前，打拳幫你贏在開打後</span>"},{"pid":"99b35d65244ce75602fb45f686a4fb391fde7c01","tid":450923,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>智利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而定去LKF既鬼 咁低汗汁既</blockquote><br />\n生蕃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e05ee74159e5fd50f561e86b6f0d908ba25aaa0","tid":450923,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"如果將個智利佬換作蝻亞人，肯定唔同哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153262bc52cdf2bbfb79718b2d3a34d6b2f53891","tid":450923,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時又笑港男廢，比人撚都唔敢還拖<br />\n依架人地敢同鬼佬打，成班垃圾連登仔淨係識笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比著你地班垃圾比鬼佬撚實喊住番屋企上連登哭訴</blockquote><br />\n打輸左咪俾人笑囉<br />\n贏左點會笑"},{"pid":"418b8a00de234bd765b61cd882a49ddbb1097fc6","tid":450923,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T01:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唉 香港人幾時先可